s  Advertisement  Advertise with us  PARIS (AP) - Laurie Hernandez pauses briefly and taps her head.\", \"from\": 886, \"to\": 1259, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1119, \"end\": 1138, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Winnipeg_Free_Press\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Winnipeg Free Press\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Winnipeg_Free_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Winnipeg_Free_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 1203, \"end\": 1205, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999999748770282, \"rank\": 2.5123046471069725e-08, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 1209, \"end\": 1225, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurie_Hernandez\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Laurie Hernandez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurie_Hernandez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurie_Hernandez\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read this article for free:    Already have an account?Log in here \\u00bb  To continue reading, please subscribe:  $0 for the first 4 weeks*  *No charge for 4 weeks then price increases to the regular rate of $19.00 plus GST every four weeks.\", \"from\": 1261, \"to\": 1498, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Offer available to new and qualified returning subscribers only.\", \"from\": 1499, \"to\": 1563, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Cancel any time.\", \"from\": 1564, \"to\": 1580, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"$4.75/week*  *Billed as $19 plus GST every four weeks.\", \"from\": 1582, \"to\": 1636, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Cancel any time.\", \"from\": 1637, \"to\": 1653, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To continue reading, please subscribe:  $1 for the first 4 weeks*  No thanks  *Your next subscription payment will increase by $1.00 and you will be charged $16.99 plus GST for four weeks.\", \"from\": 1655, \"to\": 1843, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After four weeks, your payment will increase to $23.99 plus GST every four weeks.\", \"from\": 1844, \"to\": 1925, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"PARIS (AP) - Laurie Hernandez pauses briefly and taps her head.\", \"from\": 1927, \"to\": 1990, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1934, \"end\": 1936, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999999748770282, \"rank\": 2.5123046471069725e-08, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 1940, \"end\": 1956, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurie_Hernandez\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Laurie Hernandez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurie_Hernandez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurie_Hernandez\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read unlimited articles for free today:    Already have an account?Log in here \\u00bb  Hey there, time traveller!This article was published04/08/2024(485 days ago), so information in it may no longer be current.\", \"from\": 1992, \"to\": 2198, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"PARIS (AP) - Laurie Hernandez pauses briefly and taps her head.\", \"from\": 2200, \"to\": 2263, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2207, \"end\": 2209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999999748770282, \"rank\": 2.5123046471069725e-08, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 2213, \"end\": 2229, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurie_Hernandez\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Laurie Hernandez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurie_Hernandez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurie_Hernandez\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is a lot going on in here,\\\" the two-time Olympic gymnastics medalist turned TV analyst said with a laugh.\", \"from\": 2265, \"to\": 2377, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is a lot of chatter.\\\"\", \"from\": 2378, \"to\": 2406, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yes, there is.\", \"from\": 2408, \"to\": 2422, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And whatever gets through the filter - which, to be clear, is most of it - has helped make the 24-year-old's foray into commentating a hit with both TV viewers and those like Hernandez who are perennially online.\", \"from\": 2424, \"to\": 2636, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2599, \"end\": 2608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hernandez_(wrestler)\", \"score\": 0.7544329697359324, \"rank\": 0.12361940355195014, \"text\": \"Hernandez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hernandez_(wrestler)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hernandez_(wrestler)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Eight years ago in Rio de Janeiro, she was the youngest member of the Simone Biles -led \\\"Final Five\\\" team that stormed to the gold medal.\", \"from\": 2638, \"to\": 2775, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2657, \"end\": 2671, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.014107229535042e-19, \"text\": \"Rio de Janeiro\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}, {\"begin\": 2708, \"end\": 2720, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hernandez added a silver on beam later in those Games, where her boundless energy helped make her a breakout star.\", \"from\": 2776, \"to\": 2890, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2776, \"end\": 2785, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hernandez_(wrestler)\", \"score\": 0.7544329697359324, \"rank\": 0.12361940355195014, \"text\": \"Hernandez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hernandez_(wrestler)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hernandez_(wrestler)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not much has changed in Paris other than Hernandez's point of view.\", \"from\": 2892, \"to\": 2959, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2916, \"end\": 2921, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.556285327685436e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2933, \"end\": 2942, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hernandez_(wrestler)\", \"score\": 0.7544329697359324, \"rank\": 0.12361940355195014, \"text\": \"Hernandez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hernandez_(wrestler)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hernandez_(wrestler)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are nerves to be sure when she slips her headset on alongside broadcast partner Rich Lerner, just very different ones than the kind she experienced as an athlete.\", \"from\": 2961, \"to\": 3129, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3047, \"end\": 3051, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rich_Hardbeck\", \"score\": 0.9999999997412488, \"rank\": 2.3034941407335261e-10, \"text\": \"Rich\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rich_Hardbeck\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rich_Hardbeck\"}, {\"begin\": 3052, \"end\": 3058, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abba_P._Lerner\", \"score\": 0.9999254680629297, \"rank\": 6.651469486310307e-05, \"text\": \"Lerner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q188094\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abba_P._Lerner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abba_P._Lerner\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet when she starts to talk, the affection she still feels for her sport well into her retirement is obvious.\", \"from\": 3131, \"to\": 3240, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So is the wonder that creeps into her commentary when the camera happens to catch someone famous in the stands, as it did during the women's all-around finals when actor/comedian Seth Rogen popped up on the monitor in front of Hernandez's spot in the media tribune inside Bercy Arena.\", \"from\": 3241, \"to\": 3525, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3420, \"end\": 3430, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seth_Rogen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Seth Rogen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seth_Rogen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seth_Rogen\"}, {\"begin\": 3468, \"end\": 3477, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hernandez_(wrestler)\", \"score\": 0.7544329697359324, \"rank\": 0.12361940355195014, \"text\": \"Hernandez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hernandez_(wrestler)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hernandez_(wrestler)\"}, {\"begin\": 3513, \"end\": 3524, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Accor_Arena\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bercy Arena\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Accor_Arena\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Accor_Arena\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Of all the people you could cut to?\", \"from\": 3527, \"to\": 3563, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Like, that's so cool,\\\" Hernandez said.\", \"from\": 3564, \"to\": 3602, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3587, \"end\": 3596, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hernandez_(wrestler)\", \"score\": 0.7544329697359324, \"rank\": 0.12361940355195014, \"text\": \"Hernandez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hernandez_(wrestler)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hernandez_(wrestler)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But, like, I just would not expect, like, Seth Rogen to go to gymnastics.\\\"\", \"from\": 3603, \"to\": 3678, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3646, \"end\": 3656, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seth_Rogen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Seth Rogen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seth_Rogen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seth_Rogen\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Call that the \\\"Biles effect.\\\"\", \"from\": 3680, \"to\": 3709, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What's happening during the competition on screens - TVs, phone or otherwise - back in the U.S. might best be described as the \\\"Hernandez effect.\\\"\", \"from\": 3710, \"to\": 3856, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3838, \"end\": 3847, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hernandez_(wrestler)\", \"score\": 0.7544329697359324, \"rank\": 0.12361940355195014, \"text\": \"Hernandez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hernandez_(wrestler)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hernandez_(wrestler)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She mixes empathy, education and laughter with equal measure.\", \"from\": 3858, \"to\": 3919, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She spent a decade inside a sport that at times can take far more than it gives.\", \"from\": 3920, \"to\": 4000, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Those memories are never too far away, and they have help inform her approach.\", \"from\": 4001, \"to\": 4079, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not know many sports, you know, who are like, 'Oh, I fear for my life every time I turn,'\\\" Hernandez said.\", \"from\": 4081, \"to\": 4193, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4178, \"end\": 4187, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hernandez_(wrestler)\", \"score\": 0.7544329697359324, \"rank\": 0.12361940355195014, \"text\": \"Hernandez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hernandez_(wrestler)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hernandez_(wrestler)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And because of that, she's careful to note mistakes but not harp on them.\", \"from\": 4195, \"to\": 4268, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's gymnastics.\", \"from\": 4269, \"to\": 4285, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Perfection is unattainable.\", \"from\": 4286, \"to\": 4313, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So why place that level of expectation on athletes doing the hardest skills ever done?\", \"from\": 4314, \"to\": 4400, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Wobbles and falls are as much a part of the sport as leotards and chalk.\", \"from\": 4402, \"to\": 4474, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They are inevitable.\", \"from\": 4475, \"to\": 4495, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She prefers to explain how they happened so viewers who might only stumble across it once every four years understand.\", \"from\": 4496, \"to\": 4614, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The same goes for when routines are done exquisitely.\", \"from\": 4616, \"to\": 4669, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sometimes what the viewer sees and the judges see are different things and when the score flashes there is a \\\"wait, what?\\\"\", \"from\": 4670, \"to\": 4792, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"element involved.\", \"from\": 4793, \"to\": 4810, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Welcome to the world of what she's calling \\\"ghost deductions.\\\"\", \"from\": 4812, \"to\": 4874, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To the naked eye, this looks like the most marvelous thing, and it is,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 4876, \"to\": 4958, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But there are deductions that you cannot see at home that I can see or the judges can see, and it's up to you to just listen to it or not.\\\"\", \"from\": 4959, \"to\": 5099, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The gymnasts are not the only ones being judged.\", \"from\": 5101, \"to\": 5149, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hernandez would love to tell you she buries her phone in her pocket and ignores whatever capital T \\\"Thoughts\\\" social media might have on her performance.\", \"from\": 5150, \"to\": 5303, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5150, \"end\": 5159, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hernandez_(wrestler)\", \"score\": 0.7544329697359324, \"rank\": 0.12361940355195014, \"text\": \"Hernandez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hernandez_(wrestler)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hernandez_(wrestler)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She can not.\", \"from\": 5304, \"to\": 5316, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She's Gen Z.\", \"from\": 5317, \"to\": 5329, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5323, \"end\": 5328, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Generation_Z\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gen Z\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Generation_Z\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Generation_Z\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At this point in her life, it's practically in her DNA.\", \"from\": 5330, \"to\": 5385, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She's not afraid to clap back at critics if only to respectfully ask they simply not tag her in their posts so she can scroll in peace.\", \"from\": 5386, \"to\": 5521, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Weekly  A weekly look at what's happening in Winnipeg's arts and entertainment scene.\", \"from\": 5523, \"to\": 5608, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There will be times when something happens in front of her and some reference - be it from TikTok or elsewhere - will pop into her head and it transforms from thought to her microphone in a flash.\", \"from\": 5610, \"to\": 5806, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5701, \"end\": 5707, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.398860623641243e-42, \"text\": \"TikTok\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Is it \\\"unprofessional\\\" as she put it?\", \"from\": 5808, \"to\": 5845, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Not really.\", \"from\": 5846, \"to\": 5857, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's her way of trying to stay as authentic as possible.\", \"from\": 5858, \"to\": 5914, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When she gets nervous - and she does - she imagines she's sitting on a couch at a party.\", \"from\": 5915, \"to\": 6003, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everyone's got a glass of whatever you want and we all just happen to be like, besties hanging out,\\\" Hernandez said.\", \"from\": 6005, \"to\": 6122, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6107, \"end\": 6116, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hernandez_(wrestler)\", \"score\": 0.7544329697359324, \"rank\": 0.12361940355195014, \"text\": \"Hernandez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hernandez_(wrestler)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hernandez_(wrestler)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And I just happen to know a lot about the thing that's on TV.\\\"\", \"from\": 6123, \"to\": 6186, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"___  AP Summer Olympics: https://apnews.com/hub/2024-paris-olympic-games  AdvertisementAdvertise With Us  AdvertisementAdvertise With Us  Advertisement  Learn more about Winnipeg Free Press Advertising solutions\", \"from\": 6188, \"to\": 6399, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6193, \"end\": 6195, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999999748770282, \"rank\": 2.5123046471069725e-08, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 6358, \"end\": 6377, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Winnipeg_Free_Press\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Winnipeg Free Press\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Winnipeg_Free_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Winnipeg_Free_Press\"}]}]}"